{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>人員接報到場，39歲姓馮男子昏迷被送往北區醫院搶救，其後被證實死亡。據了解，事主患有身體疾病。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260318/1110941835783704576841703.jpeg/s07-Yl9OJXirDbj7TzTOlb5CSVozhLLpxRIYQcUSGEE\" alt=\"北區醫院。（資料圖片）\"><figcaption>北區醫院。（資料圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-21T09:20:11.575169+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":59,"images":1,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}